reviewText: There are clips from youtbe that i Have already seen, and the whole dvd is like 20 mintues long, which i felt was a waste of money. I could have made a dvd of dmx careers and life from youtube and put them on dvd with a story line. There was nothing unleahed about dmx, stuff we already know or have talked about and seen. Im not going to send it back, I am going to take it over my aunts and sit it somewhere in the house and jsut leave it there, im sure they will do something to it.
